SD.1 StructureDefinition-pdexplanpractitioner

title: StructureDefinition-pdexplanpractitioner-intro layout: default active: StructureDefinition-pdexplanpractitioner-intro —

A Health Plan SHOULD provide the following minimum fields:

  • Human Name
  • ContactPoint
